name: What happened?
description: To love is to suffer. In order not to suffer, one must not love. But then you will suffer from what you do not love. Therefore, to love is to suffer. But not to love also means suffering. And to suffer is to suffer. To be happy means you have to love. It means you have to suffer, but suffering makes a person unhappy. Therefore, in order to be unhappy, one must love, or love, in order to suffer, or to suffer from an excess of happiness.
